# Project Description
This project contains source files, notes and everything collected and sourced in the process of
wiritng a paper on this topic. The goal of this paper is to be an introductory material for anyone
with a background in elementary numerical analysis and at least one imperative programming language
interested in learning what does functional programming, especially Haskell has to offer in this
field.

